PrecisAmendments respecting chapters 115 and 119 of the QUEEN'S REGULATIONS AND ORDERS FOR THE CANADIAN FORCES to regulate the stay of proceedings inquiry procedures for an accused person found to be unfit to stand trial, as well as enhance the impartiality of the military justice system.
